<tamination title="Ferris Wheel">

  <tam title="Ferris Wheel"
       from="Right-Handed Two-Faced Lines, strictly"
       formation="Two-Faced Lines RH" difficulty="1">
    <path>
      <move select="Forward 2" hands="right"/>
      <move select="Run Right" beats="4" hands="gripright" scaleX="1" scaleY="2" offsetX="1" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="Forward 2" hands="left"/>
      <move select="U-Turn Right" beats="4" hands="gripleft" offsetX="1" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="U-Turn Right" beats="4" hands="gripleft" offsetX="1" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="Run Right" beats="4" hands="gripright" scaleX="2" scaleY="2" offsetX="1" />
    </path>
    <taminator>The center couples form a momentary two-faced line, following
    the Dance action description.
    </taminator>
  </tam>



  <tam title="Ferris Wheel"
       from="Right-Handed Two-Faced Lines"
       formation="Two-Faced Lines RH"
       fractions="" difficulty="1">
    <path>
      <move select="Run Right" beats="4" hands="gripright" scaleX="2" scaleY="2" offsetX="3" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="U-Turn Right" beats="4" hands="gripleft" offsetX="3" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="U-Turn Right" beats="4" hands="gripleft" offsetX="1" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="Run Right" beats="4" hands="gripright" scaleX="2" scaleY="2" offsetX="1" />
    </path>
    <taminator>The center dancers start the Wheel and Deal action immmediately,
       and a two-faced line is not formed.  This is how many dancers perform this call.
    </taminator>
  </tam>

  <tam title="Ferris Wheel"
       from="Left-Handed Two-Faced Lines"
       formation="Two-Faced Lines LH"
       fractions="" difficulty="1">
    <path>
      <move select="Run Left" beats="4" hands="gripleft" scaleX="2" scaleY="2" offsetX="1" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="U-Turn Left" beats="4" hands="gripright" offsetX="1" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="U-Turn Left" beats="4" hands="gripright" offsetX="3" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="Run Left" beats="4" hands="gripleft" scaleX="2" scaleY="2" offsetX="3" />
    </path>
  </tam>

  <tam title="Ferris Wheel"
       from="T-Bone Couples"
       formation="T-Bone Couples"
       fractions="" difficulty="2">
    <path>
      <move select="Run Right" beats="4" hands="gripright" scaleX="2" scaleY="2" offsetX="3" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="U-Turn Right" beats="4" hands="gripleft" offsetX="3" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="Run Left" beats="4" hands="gripleft" scaleX="2" scaleY="2" offsetX="1" />
    </path>
    <path>
      <move select="U-Turn Left" beats="4" hands="gripright" offsetX="1" />
    </path>
  </tam>
</tamination>
